<div id="ta189_85" class="block iDevice_content">
<div class="dentro_contenidos" style="display: block;" id="pagina_1">
<p>This part consists on a <b>word formation</b> exercise to evaluate the students lexical and lexico-grammatical knowledge.</p>
<p>The aim is to fill a series of gaps in a text. The stem of the missing words are provided in order to be used once changed to fit in the sentence.</p>
<p>Tips:</p>
<ul>
<li>First read the text quickly to get an idea of what it is about.</li>
<li>Then, decide what type of word you need and think about whether it’s singular or plural.</li>
<li>When you have finished check your answers reading the whole text again.</li>
<li>Make sure you put the verbs in the right form.</li>
<li>Be careful to spell your answers correctly</li>
</ul>
